      "content": "makes sense. we're also worried about potential cargo theft or stuff going missing in transit. with these maritime routes, are there any particular types of unforeseen loss or 'mysteries' we should be prepared for in our insurance claims? like, what's usually categorized as an unavoidable maritime casualty?",
